room_title: Escape room "Quest for Excalibur" by Lock and Key Escape in Minneapolis - St. Paul
room_description: Camelot is in chaos. King Arthur has disappeared and the knights of the round table have scattered. Fear runs rampant across the land. The mighty wizard Merlin has created a new quest to find loyal servants who are willing to help restore order. Any group willing to prove that they are worthy must do so by completing Merlinâ€™s trials and pulling King Aruthur famed sword Excalibur from the stone. The fate of Camelot rests in your hands.
